title: What are the collection figures of 10 Endrathukulla and Naanum Rowdy Dhaan?
text:
Here's the buzz on the box office figures of the two Ayudha pooja releases â€” 10 Endrathukulla and Naanum Rowdy Dhaan. Dhanush has tweeted the first-day collections of his production, the Vijay-Sethupathi-starrer Naanum Rowdy Dhaan. 

"Naanum Rowdy dhaan opens to a superb 2.16cr day 1 .Highest for Vijay Sethupathi. Expecting a big jump today," he tweeted and gave area-wise break-up of the collections. 

Meanwhile, there are two versions on the collections of Vikram's 10 Endrathukulla. While some trade analysts are saying that the film has collected to the tune of Rs 6.5 crore, making it the second highest opening day figures for a Vikram film after I, some others are maintaining that the film has collected only Rs 2.91 crores. Now, it is up to the production house behind the film to come out and clarify on the actual figures. But with the film earning mixed reviews, will they?
